d the county to be organized on april   an additional act clarified the county’s status on january   and the county was finally organized later during that year  the railroad changed ownership and names more than once and was also known as the lake erie and western railroad the nickel plate road and the norfolk and western railway the line is currently owned by the norfolk southern railway  hartford citys workforce became an attraction for glass companies the city had a community of highly skilled glass workers from belgium  a second source says the american window glass plant closed in  instead of   grants overhead door articledead link in volume  of the international directory of company histories has been reproduced on a web page  in the united states census bureaus american fact finder  use quick start select blackford county indiana for geography and dp profile of selected economic characteristics  for topic or table name  in the united states census bureaus american fact finder  use quick start select blackford county indiana for geography and dp profile of selected social characteristics  for topic or table name  blackford countys  square miles multiplied by  acres per square mile is  acres  ha the countys farmland totals to  acres  ha the amount of farmland divided by the countys total of  acres  ha is  percent  examples of johnsons patents are united states patent no  united states patent no  and united states patent no  referencesedit  origin of indiana county names indiana historical bureau retrieved    a biography of isaac newton blackford blackford county historical society retrieved    a b find a county national association of counties archived from the original on  retrieved    stats indiana blackford county townships indiana business research center indiana university kelly school of business retrieved    a b census  us gazetteer files counties united states census archived from the original on  retrieved    a b c blackford county quickfacts united s